---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Cancellation & Refund Policy">
    <!-- Legal Content -->
    <section class="legal-content">
        <h1>Refund <span class="accent">Policy</span></h1>
        <p class="legal-meta">Last Updated: February 6, 2026</p>

        <div class="callout callout-important">
            <strong>Important:</strong> Due to the nature of digital software products, all sales of GemCrest are final.
            Please review this policy carefully before making a purchase.
        </div>

        <h2>No Refund Policy</h2>
        <p>
            GemCrest is a digital software product. Once a license key is generated and delivered, we cannot offer
            refunds as the product cannot be "returned" in the traditional sense.
        </p>

        <h2>Before You Purchase</h2>
        <p>We encourage you to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Review all features on our <a href="/gemcrest"
                    style="color:var(--rose-gold);">product page</a>
            </li>
            <li>Read the <a href="/docs" style="color:var(--rose-gold);">documentation</a>
                thoroughly
            </li>
            <li>Check <a href="/docs/getting-started" style="color:var(--rose-gold);">system
                    requirements</a>
            </li>
            <li>Review <a href="/docs/faq" style="color:var(--rose-gold);">frequently asked
                    questions</a></li>
            <li>Contact us with any questions before purchasing</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Exceptions</h2>
        <p>We may consider refunds only in the following circumstances:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Duplicate Purchase:</strong> If you accidentally purchased twice, we will refund the duplicate
            </li>
            <li><strong>Technical Issues:</strong> If the software fails to function on a compatible system and we
                cannot resolve the issue</li>
            <li><strong>Non-Delivery:</strong> If you did not receive your license key within 24 hours of purchase</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How to Request</h2>
        <p>
            If you believe you qualify for an exception, please contact us within 7 days of purchase at <a
                href="mailto:aravcrestlabs@proton.me" style="color:var(--rose-gold);">aravcrestlabs@proton.me</a>
            with:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Your order ID or payment receipt</li>
            <li>Email used for purchase</li>
            <li>Detailed description of the issue</li>
            <li>Screenshots or error messages (if applicable)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Processing Time</h2>
        <p>
            If a refund is approved, it will be processed within 5-7 business days. The amount will be credited to your
            original payment method.
        </p>

        <h2>License Revocation</h2>
        <p>
            If a refund is issued, your license key will be revoked and you must uninstall the software immediately.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
            For refund inquiries, please contact:<br>
            <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:aravcrestlabs@proton.me"
                style="color:var(--rose-gold);">aravcrestlabs@proton.me</a>
        </p>
    </section>
</Layout>
